400
00:20:31.666 --> 00:20:33.000
窶ｪDon't insult me.

401
00:20:33.083 --> 00:20:34.458
窶ｪI'm insulting you?

402
00:20:53.208 --> 00:20:55.416
窶ｪI want you to return Mpume's phone.

403
00:20:55.500 --> 00:20:57.791
窶ｪBut Ma. I don't know
窶ｪwhere Mpume's phone is. though.

404
00:20:57.875 --> 00:20:58.875
窶ｪSarah.

405
00:21:04.125 --> 00:21:05.125
窶ｪLook at me.

406
00:21:07.750 --> 00:21:09.125
窶ｪ[exhales sharply]

407
00:21:18.500 --> 00:21:20.291
窶ｪ[gqom music playing on headphones]

408
00:21:20.375 --> 00:21:21.375
窶ｪ[clears throat]

409
00:21:26.000 --> 00:21:27.583
窶ｪ[Jonasi] Listen here. boy.

410
00:21:27.666 --> 00:21:28.666
窶ｪ[music stops]

411
00:21:29.375 --> 00:21:30.791
窶ｪWhy did you窶ｦ

412
00:21:31.791 --> 00:21:35.916
窶ｪlet Mpume and her friends
窶ｪturn my house into a madhouse?

413
00:21:36.666 --> 00:21:37.958
窶ｪ[Joyce] Jonasi.

414
00:21:38.041 --> 00:21:40.583
窶ｪ-I thought we already spoke about this?
窶ｪ-No. love.

415
00:21:41.666 --> 00:21:43.333
窶ｪI want Menzi to answer.

416
00:21:45.458 --> 00:21:49.958
窶ｪ[stammering] Yes. Dad.
窶ｪI tried to stop them. You can ask Mpume.

417
00:21:50.041 --> 00:21:52.041
窶ｪ-Mpume!
窶ｪ-[Jonasi] I'm asking you.

418
00:21:52.625 --> 00:21:54.375
窶ｪYou're the firstborn son.

419
00:21:54.458 --> 00:21:58.958
窶ｪSo why are you acting weak
窶ｪwhen you're my son?

420
00:21:59.041 --> 00:22:01.416
窶ｪYou haven't been the man
窶ｪof this house for the entire year.

421
00:22:01.500 --> 00:22:02.916
窶ｪAt least Menzi's trying.

422
00:22:03.416 --> 00:22:05.125
窶ｪ[suspenseful music playing]

423
00:22:05.208 --> 00:22:06.208
窶ｪExcuse me?

424
00:22:08.791 --> 00:22:10.166
窶ｪWhat did you say to me?

425
00:22:11.500 --> 00:22:12.791
窶ｪMy love.

426
00:22:12.875 --> 00:22:15.583
窶ｪ-Who do you think you're talking to?
窶ｪ-Oh. you want to be a father now?

427
00:22:15.666 --> 00:22:16.958
窶ｪYou walked out on us. Dad.

428
00:22:17.041 --> 00:22:18.333
窶ｪHave you forgotten?

429
00:22:21.208 --> 00:22:22.208
窶ｪ[scoffs]

430
00:22:34.875 --> 00:22:36.458
窶ｪHmm. [sniffles]

431
00:22:37.666 --> 00:22:39.208
窶ｪ[sighs] I've seen it all.

432
00:22:40.458 --> 00:22:41.458
窶ｪ[exhales sharply]

433
00:22:42.583 --> 00:22:44.583
窶ｪHow the mighty have fallen.

434
00:22:46.750 --> 00:22:47.750
窶ｪ[scoffs]

435
00:22:53.833 --> 00:22:55.541
窶ｪ-[glass shatters]
窶ｪ-[Joyce] Jo!

436
00:22:55.625 --> 00:22:57.166
窶ｪ[dramatic music playing]

437
00:22:57.250 --> 00:22:59.250
窶ｪDon't you ever talk to me like that.
窶ｪUnderstood?

438
00:22:59.333 --> 00:23:00.333
窶ｪJonasi.

439
00:23:00.416 --> 00:23:02.000
窶ｪ[Jonasi] I'm not one of your buddies!

440
00:23:02.583 --> 00:23:04.125
窶ｪDo you hear me. Mpume?

441
00:23:08.541 --> 00:23:11.166
窶ｪYou. stop being a weakling.

442
00:23:12.500 --> 00:23:13.708
窶ｪToughen up.

443
00:23:14.583 --> 00:23:15.875
窶ｪ-Stand up when I'm talking to you!
窶ｪ-Stop!

444
00:23:15.958 --> 00:23:18.000
窶ｪ-Stop being weak!
窶ｪ-Leave him alone!

445
00:23:18.083 --> 00:23:19.875
窶ｪ[distorted clamoring]

446
00:23:20.541 --> 00:23:21.833
窶ｪYou're hurting him!

447
00:23:21.916 --> 00:23:24.375
窶ｪ-Jonasi. stop!
窶ｪ-[breathing heavily]

448
00:23:26.166 --> 00:23:28.208
窶ｪ[Mpume] Do you really wanna kill him?

449
00:23:30.916 --> 00:23:32.166
窶ｪ-[coughing]
窶ｪ-Menzi. are you okay?

450
00:23:33.125 --> 00:23:34.250
窶ｪAre you okay. bro?

451
00:23:35.500 --> 00:23:38.000
窶ｪ-[door slams]
窶ｪ-[Menzi breathing heavily]

452
00:23:38.083 --> 00:23:39.666
窶ｪIt's going to be okay.

453
00:23:40.916 --> 00:23:41.916
窶ｪIt's okay.

454
00:23:42.416 --> 00:23:45.083
窶ｪ[both sobbing]

455
00:23:47.875 --> 00:23:49.208
窶ｪIt's okay.

456
00:23:50.458 --> 00:23:53.875
窶ｪ-[sobbing continues]
窶ｪ-It's okay. my boy.
